Treasury balances at the FederalReserve rose on Feb 27 to 3.482 billion dlrs from 1.538 billiondlrs the previous business day, the Treasury said in its latestbudget statement.    Balances in tax and loan note accounts fell to 21.334billion dlrs from 25.164 billion dlrs on the same respectivedays.    The Treasury's operating cash balance totaled 24.816billion dlrs on Feb 27 compared with 26.702 billion dlrs on Feb26. Reuter&#3;